done-so-far: Root-caused "unbound global: httpClient" on ssc run (v2 VM). The fast http plugin registers httpClient/httpTimeout/httpRetry as natives, but PluginBridge only gives httpGet/httpPost a *global* binding for the batch/ssc-run env, so the scoped client-config intrinsics are unreachable. Fix: mirror the httpGet/httpPost registerGlobal delegation for httpClient/httpTimeout/httpRetry in PluginBridge.
